  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd, \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "In Mannar, private bus owners, three-wheeler drivers are protesting for fuel",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "In Mannar, since the morning of Monday, 05th, the people have suffered massively due to the protest carried out by the Mannar private bus association and tricycle drivers separately demanding fuel.",
        "The private bus owners blocked the road to prevent the government transport service from proceeding.",
        "It was requested by the concerned party to supply 13200 liters of diesel to Mannar District Private Transport Association buses.",
        "However, out of the 13200 liters of diesel supplied, only 2413 liters of diesel was supplied to private buses.",
        "The private bus association owners requested diesel from the Mannar depot authorities but it was not provided.",
        "In this situation, since today (5) morning, the private buses have been engaged in work inspection, they have blocked the road with the private buses so that they cannot run the government transport service and they have also demanded to provide fuel for them.",
        "As a result, transport services were completely disrupted for some time and people faced various inconveniences.",
        "In this situation, a special discussion took place today at 10 am in the Mannar District Secretariat under the leadership of the Government President Mrs. A. Sranli D Mel and representatives of the government and private transport associations.",
        "During the discussion, it was agreed that according to the government's position of supplying diesel to private bus service buses from Sri Lanka Transport Council's oil tanks, if 6600 liters of diesel is supplied to Mannar Road, 2500 liters of diesel and 5000 liters of diesel if 13,200 liters of diesel is supplied to private bus services.",
        "In this situation, the boycott protest initiated by the private bus association owners was abandoned.",
        "At the same time, it is also noteworthy that the three-wheeler drivers engaged in service in Mannar are protesting for proper supply of fuel."
      ],
